{% extends "core/emails/base.html.j2" %}
{% block title %}Welcome to sbomify{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
    <h1>Welcome to sbomify, {{ user.first_name|default:user.username }}!</h1>
    <p>
        Thanks for signing up. sbomify helps you manage your security artifacts
        like SBOMs, track vulnerabilities, and meet compliance requirements, all in one place.
    </p>
    <p>To get started, head to your dashboard and create your first product.</p>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
        <a href="{{ app_base_url }}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </p>
    <p>
        We'd love to hear what brought you to sbomify. Whether it's compliance,
        vulnerability tracking, or something else entirely, just reply to this
        email and let us know.
    </p>
    <p>
        New to SBOMs? Learn <a href="https://sbomify.com/what-is-sbom/">what an SBOM is and why it matters</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-secondary">
        sbomify is open source, so you can always
        <a href="https://github.com/sbomify/sbomify/">self-host it for free</a>.
        Our hosted version offers a free Community tier, a Business plan
        {% if is_trial %}(you're starting with a {{ TRIAL_PERIOD_DAYS }}-day trial){% endif %}
        ,
        and an Enterprise plan for larger teams.
    </p>
{% endblock %}
{% block signoff %}
    <p>
        Welcome aboard!
        <br>
        <strong>Viktor and the sbomify Team</strong>
    </p>
{% endblock %}
